name: Queen of Angels Catholic Church
review_text:
Queen of Angels in western Riverside area is a beautiful church located between residencies.

Although I am not a regular parishioner here, I have attended Mass as a visiting guest musician for my friend‚Äôs wedding, various rehearsals, and another special event Mass held by the diocese.

The layout of the church is circular and the font is at the back. Entering the church, you have a view of the beautiful altar and large crucifix, and the choir section off to the left.

Being so spacious, the acoustics can sound a bit sloppy but given the right sound system settings, it can sound beautiful.

There are plenty of parking spaces here.

Overall, very beautiful church for prayer and worship.

name: Queen of Angels Catholic Church
review_text: The church physically is so beautiful. It‚Äôs well taken care of. My husband and I got married in October 21 2021. The process was not the easiest. At least they don‚Äôt make it easy. There is a lack of communication that really creates more stress than anything. To say a few, we were not told about the music system (you need to have a live band they don‚Äôt play recordings), we were not told about all the requirements needed to complete our marital blessings, we were not prepared for the actual ceremony (the priest expected more of us than what we were prepared for). Everything was last minute information. We were also told 1 DAY before the wedding that our witnesses had to be interviewed. On top of that the priest refused to interview my second witness who took time out of work to go to the interview because ‚Äúhe was busy‚Äù (personal I believe he just didn‚Äôt want to) even though I made it aware what time my witnesses were going and he took it upon himself to choose the second witness for me. I was very upset about that. If I could do it all over again, I would not marry here. Their communication can improve, but the whole situation with the witness was just plain wrong. I do not recommend it for weddings but I do for normal mass.
